<p>I have p:tabmenu component with three tabs.When user clicks on a tab I am displaying p:accordionpanel.Under each accordion panel i have list of tabs where in each tab displays P:datatable.I have problem when user changes tabs in P:tabmenu.Below is the scenario.</p>  <p>1)User clicks on tab1 from P:tabmenu and sorts/navigates data table which is inside p:accordionpanel 2)User clicks on tab2 from p:tabmenu 3)When user again come back to tab1 the data table is not being reset.i.e it is displaying previously selected page/sorting order.</p>